data.description: This beautiful home features 2-stories located in River Point. It has 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an open living area with a vaulted ceiling, and a separate family/living room with a fireplace. Fenced backyard with patio area. Single car garage. It is conveniently located less than 15 minutes from Langley AFB and minutes from highways. Take a look today!
